    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jesus Lord, Jesus Lord! Why dost Thou delay?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "What prevents Thine advent? Why not come today?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Generations of saints waited all their lives;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’ve watched here, tens of years, for Thee to arrive."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Why not please cut short these lengthy yearning days?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "O Lord, heed this our plea: Come without delay."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Come without delay. Come without delay."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jesus, Lord! Jesus, Lord! Why dost Thou not come?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Since Thou went into heav’n, nothing here I love,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Days below seem as though there’s no break of dawn;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "On my face, seems no trace of a joy long gone."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Passion, drive, once alive, no more in me burn;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jesus Lord! Jesus Lord! Why don’t You return?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Why don’t You return? Why don’t You return?"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Please come back! Please come back! All around I see"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Some grow slack, some slide back, some change gradually;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Love once bold groweth cold, suff’ring takes its toll;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Faith and sighs mingled rise, forward steps are slowed;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lamp of hope dimmer grows, can’t hold out much more."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Seeing these, come back, please! Why still tarry, Lord?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Why still tarry, Lord? Why still tarry, Lord?"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jesus, Lord! Jesus, Lord! Why art Thou not here?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jesus, Lord! Jesus, Lord! Why dost not appear?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Till what date must I wait? Till what year, what day?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As I stay, watch and pray, patience ebbs away;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jesus, Lord! Jesus, Lord! Quickly come, I pray!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jesus, Lord! Jesus, Lord! Quickly come, I pray!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Quickly come, I pray! Quickly come, I pray!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    }
  ],
